name: PeakWind
0:
”Alexa, use Peak Wind to check Baltimore”
”Alexa, tell Peak Wind to check wind in Scott Key bridge”
”Alexa, use Peak Wind and give me wind info around Solomons Island”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: peak wind
des:
Using information from NOAA buoys, get information about the latest wind status. Typically, the wind status will be available within the past 10 minutes and it gets updated every 6 minutes. 

The following buoys around the Chesapeake Bay are currently supported: Baltimore, Bishops Head, Cape May, Kiptopeke, Lewes, Ocean City, Scott Key Bridge, Solomons Island, and Tolchester.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
